Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极快的剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在厉害 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在火时针指向十二点前打倒我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是过于狂妄了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何称呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波鲁纳雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就自我介绍 让·皮埃尔·波鲁纳雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Merci beaucoup
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你的自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波鲁纳雷夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(740,660)}Monsieur
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请勿把我的火焰理解为大自然的火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不会总是往上烧或者顺风烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为能自由自在地操纵火焰 才被称为红色魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界起源于一片火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是暗示起始 操纵一切起源的火焰的红色魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你说我狂妄？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我的剑法…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狂妄！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一剑刺串5枚硬币 就在硬币重合的瞬间！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 硬币之间还夹着一团火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很清楚这意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着我的替身甚至能自由自在地切断火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它能切断空气 在空气和空气间制造出间隔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你的火焰在我的银色战车前完全不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的替身——战车的卡牌 暗示着侵略和胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这个狭窄的地方解决你也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 阿布德尔 你的火焰在宽阔的地方更能发挥威力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种地方打倒你 才是我的替身值得骄傲的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人出来！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:53.52,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}そして、集いしスターダスト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.08,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}100年目の目醒めに呼ばれて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}男たちは向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:10.58,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}時の砂を越えるJourney
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:16.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}鎖のよう連なる 絡み合う宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:16.71,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:22.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:22.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:22.93,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.74,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.98,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}打ち込むのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:32.60,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}All right now All right now All right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.09,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}誇りのBullet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.39,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:47.28,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:53.52,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的苏醒在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.08,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星尘遥呼 相继汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子汉一行已启程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:10.58,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越时间的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:16.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串错综连横的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:22.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挥起白金斩断命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.98,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迸射而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.09,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是高傲的弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:47.28,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铁拳百裂 神圣的幻象 Stand Proud!
